  "title": "Van Driver",
  "description": "<p>Class 3 Delivery Driver Needed.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Work Location Based in West Coast Drive.</p>\n<p>Deliver catering items including food and kitchenware.</p>\n<p>Load and unload items.</p>\n<p>Deliver to event venues island wide.</p>\n<p>Take care and maintain vehicle.</p>\n<p>Can work independently and can plan route properly.</p>\n<p>Take responsibility of items/goods at all time throughout delivery process.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>Holds a valid Class 3 driving licence.</p>\n<p>Always punctual and on time.</p>\n<p>Minimum 2 years driving experience.</p>\n<p>Able to lift heavy items.</p>\n<p>Honest and reliable.</p>",
